{"tid":1332242,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"希望可以見到22號既日出","createTime":"2019-07-19T08:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T15:59:54.000Z","uid":183582,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"05216ff884905879a93fdd72bb10e18fb027e886","tid":1332242,"uid":183582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:45:45.000Z","msg":"唔知多唔多人同我一樣諗法<br />\n老實講<br />\n我真係預左見唔到22號既太陽<br />\n呢幾日不停亂諗野 好驚21號後既香港會變成點<br />\n唔知仲可唔可以見到大家<br />\n但我地知道21號唔出 可能永遠都無機會出黎<br />\n我地真係好愛香港呢個家<br />\n所以21號見大家<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可！<br />\n1.）撤回逃犯修例<br />\n2.）撤回暴動定性<br />\n3.）無條件釋放被捕示威者<br />\n4.）追究警方暴力濫權<br />\n5.）香港要雙普選<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山！各自努力！不篤灰！不分化！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VQkYq4L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVQkYq4L.png&h=6da15164&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2725e6cfc8809f41dba65b595ca8e84ddf60cec","tid":1332242,"uid":223260,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:46:52.000Z","msg":"你會見到新香港"},{"pid":"258900a535eb4be02a22284a32327a6d5bb06ed7","tid":1332242,"uid":183582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f2725e6cfc8809f41dba65b595ca8e84ddf60cec","tid":1332242,"uid":223260,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:46:52.000Z","msg":"你會見到新香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:51:39.000Z","msg":"希望如大家所願"},{"pid":"09a80695f4a25b6973fa1d151fdc46f4ee7a7002","tid":1332242,"uid":183582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:53:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5aae94c307480d10d46dd88896702da5b426932","tid":1332242,"uid":15538,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7289c5f7cb1d340738f0e5e4335bc0b388d6860e","tid":1332242,"uid":201268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:55:09.000Z","msg":"<code>黎明前既黑暗係至撚黑暗</code><br />\n一齊加油呀"},{"pid"